        <p><strong>Smart technology:</strong> This technology uses devices such as linking sensors
            and other
            appliances
            that can be remotely monitored and programmed in order to be as energy efficient as
            possible and to respond to the needs of the users. Utilizing the Internet of Things (a
            network of
            internet-connected objects that are able to connect data) these objects will be able to
            collect
            data
            which then will be utilized so that every device in this network can make an autonomous
            decision
            with the
            objective of reducing wastage.</p>
        <p>A bit hard to compreend at first but basically, it's an intelligent system that act in
            the best way
            possible, for
            example lightning systems will only illuminate areas that require it or dim the light to
            an optimal
            point
            so no excess energy is consumed.</p>

