        <h2>Comparison:</h2>
        <p>In short we can conclude that technology is something that can change our world, and with it
            bring new
            challenges
            but also opportunities for the topic of sustainability. </p>
        <p>And though the rapidly needed increase for production due to increase in consumer's needs can
            cause
            massive
            problems, we can conclude that ultimately if we are to satisfy
            our needs we must also satisfy those of our ecosystem, the increase in technology is a must
            but it has
            to be
            equally focused on both.</p>
        <p>Still, In my opinion the positives do outweight the negatives, for it gives us a way to to
            keep
            everything
            sustainable both in the present and in the foreseeable future.</p>
